psalm.text:
[[Ps 77,12]]I remember the deeds of the LORD; 
yes, I remember your wonders of old.  
[[Ps 77,13]]And I meditate on your works; 
your exploits I ponder.

[[Ps 77,14]]O God, your way is holy; 
what great god is there like our God?
[[Ps 77,15]]You are the God who works wonders; 
among the peoples you have made known your power.

[[Ps 77,16]]With your strong arm you redeemed your people, 
the sons of Jacob and Joseph.
[[Ps 77,21]]You led your people like a flock 
under the care of Moses and Aaron.
